{"tid":2416470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓偉憂疫情未反映放寬措施後情況　料未來一至兩星期確診數字會上升","createTime":"2021-02-21T05:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T06:11:20.000Z","uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48dfc147e7566940e8eb9f261a1cf3e3de37a3e4","tid":2416470,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"農曆新年假期過去，政府專家顧問、港大醫學院院長梁卓偉表示，連續4日的病毒即時繁殖率和確診數字都持續上升，擔心現時數字仍未反映新年後社交距離措施放寬的情況，預計未來一至兩星期確診數字會上升，令第四波疫情未必斷尾。他呼籲市民盡量不要作報復式消費和不要有極端的聚集。另外，他出席無綫電視節目《講清講楚》時表示，接種疫苗後的保護作用，會滯後最少一至兩個月，如果太遲接種或等到有爆發時才接種，疫苗未必趕及即時起到保護作用，亦要面對供不應求的情況，呼籲市民要防患未然。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576657-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576657-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=25da829e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576657-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8fd4203c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576657-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6e5550043e6266d01377be05f5e42957c76fe0fc","tid":2416470,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"拜年開年群組：I am ready!"},{"pid":"2050d64865a33d9053397278ce8e3699cc1d04b5","tid":2416470,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫極端的聚集"},{"pid":"747b8ced14fe70d1d653a44b6c87b2848641a165","tid":2416470,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2050d64865a33d9053397278ce8e3699cc1d04b5","tid":2416470,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫極端的聚集"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass